summary:
who’s your daddy?
              As a parent, you have to give up on a lot. So, at his 
first night out in a very long time, Jeon...
caption:
who’s your daddy?

As a parent, you have to give up on a lot. So, at his first night out in a very long time, Jeon Jungkook didn’t hold back the tiniest bit. Turns out his drunk and very wild ONS happened to be Kim Taehyung, his project partner and the babysitter of his three-year-old son Jungwook.

Talking about awkward, there’s also Min Yoongi, a computer genius, who doesn’t leave his house and accidentally hires a naked housecleaner called Park Jimin, who refuses to say goodbye to the cutest dog called Holly.
